@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Us - Restaurant Profile</PageTitle>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white p-5 mb-5 rounded">
                <h1 class="text-center mb-4">DineOps - About Us</h1>
                <p class="text-center text-white mb-0">Helping restaurants build their online presence and connect with guests</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="mb-3">Who We Are</h2>
                <p>Restaurant Profile is a platform designed to help food service businesses establish a professional online presence. We provide tools that make it easy to showcase your restaurant, manage reservations, and present your menu to potential guests.</p>
                <p>Our mission is simple: to bridge the gap between restaurants and their customers by providing intuitive digital solutions that save time and increase visibility.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="mb-3">Who Is Our Platform For?</h2>
                <p>Our platform is built for any establishment where guests can reserve a table:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Restaurants and fine dining venues</li>
                    <li>Cafes and coffee shops</li>
                    <li>Bars and pubs</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Whether you are opening a new location or looking to improve your existing online presence, our platform adapts to your needs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="mb-3">Why Choose Us?</h2>
                
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                        <div class="p-4 border rounded h-100">
                            <h5>Easy Profile Creation</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0">Create a professional restaurant profile in minutes. No technical skills required.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                        <div class="p-4 border rounded h-100">
                            <h5>Online Reservations</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0">Let your guests book tables directly through your profile, 24/7.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                        <div class="p-4 border rounded h-100">
                            <h5>Centralized Management</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0">Manage all your reservations from one convenient dashboard.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                        <div class="p-4 border rounded h-100">
                            <h5>Increased Visibility</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0">Reach more potential guests and grow your customer base.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="mb-3">Our Values</h2>
                <p><strong>Simplicity First</strong> - We believe that powerful tools should be easy to use. Our platform is designed with simplicity in mind, so you can focus on what matters most: your guests.</p>
                <p><strong>Continuous Improvement</strong> - We are constantly developing new features and improvements based on feedback from restaurant owners like you. Your success drives our innovation.</p>
            </div>


            <div class="text-center mt-5">
                <a href="/homepage" class="button button--lg button--primary" style="text-decoration: none;">Go Back</a>
            </div>
        </div>
